INSERT INTO `tjournal` VALUES (1,1,'Recon','Tilly Job','2020-03-12 13:20:00','Found hidden entrance behind the pool house.\nWill need some muscle to get it open, bring a crow bar just in case.','',0),(2,1,'Clue','Tilly Job','2020-03-12 08:34:00','The murder weapon was a spoon. Died from blood loss from his eye sockets. His eyeballs are missing, they must contain the data we are looking for. Guarentee one of them was a cyber eye.','',1),(3,1,'Session','Tilly Job','2020-03-12 08:34:00','Job went well! : )\nAwarded 2000 Nuyen and 5 Karma','',0),(4,175,'Session','First real mission','2020-03-13 19:41:00','Stepford and Tsua know each other prior to start of mission from shared mission/history.\n\nLow Jack and Dantes in 2074 are new to the group and getting started on missions as a team.','',0),(5,175,'Mission','A briefing from Annie...','2020-03-13 19:58:00','5th floor of office building of the 14th street in about 2 hours for a simple mission (down town).\n\nHave to travel through a check point to get there though...IRL and without any visible excessive gear.\n\nSo disguised deck, professional gear and taser, driving myself there from the barrens\n\nAR with grid guide, coming from dwarven enclave from Aurora - CAS area\n - like Real Dee&amp;amp;amp;#039;s company that specializes in imported real meet and produce, grey market stuff\n - So so much advertising (humanist especially) despite blockers and physical billboards even above the barrens\n\nSecurity checkpoint - no alerts on ID or at the checkpoint - work request, pass through no issues.\n - Visual observation, scanned for image, signals, talk to officers, ect. ect.\n - Past this checkpoint, basic tracking of all people and movement expected, using automation\n - Could spoof the signals or let it ride and decide not to spoof it to avoid drawing any extra attention\n\nArrive at a Law Office &amp;amp;quot;Lynwoods Holding Co&amp;amp;quot;, with visible security present (nothing more than armored clothes or pistols allowed), 5th floor being renovated and is the site of the meeting, everyone meets at the lobby.\n\nUp on the 5th floor is construction equipment and one generic west coast human in a grey suit along with his muscle, a huge troll all cyber&amp;#039;d up and a dwarf who has similar markings to Tsua (spider).\n\nSecurity contract on building Corporate Defense Co (or subcontractor), Mr. G only cares about shipping order info but does not care about any other resources scavenged.','',0),(6,1,'Meeting','Pumpkin Job','2020-03-26 12:57:00','Johnson gave a new job, steal the golden pumpkin.\nRecommends bringing a Mage.','',0),(7,1,'Recon','Pumpkin Job','2020-03-26 12:59:00','Found entry to facility through the roof, unguarded but has Magical Barrier,\nThe whole place stinks of magic.\nOur mage better be ready.','',0),(8,1,'Clue','Pumpkin Job','2020-03-26 13:17:00','Found a piece of the Pumpkin on the 34th floor.','',0),(9,43,'Event','Rounded Up','2075-03-13 04:40:00','You&#039;ll see.','',0),(10,1,'Meeting','Tilly Job','2020-04-23 10:48:00','Meet is at a private dock. Fixer will comm us with instructions once we are there.','',0),(11,198,'Test','Test','2020-04-23 17:39:00','Test','',0),(12,198,'Test2','Test2','2020-04-23 17:39:00','Test2','',0),(13,200,'Fight','Fight 1','2020-04-29 18:29:00','Rene burstet\n5 Erfolge','',0);
